show.description: When her father names the irresponsible Jonas as heir to their empire, Emma launches a bold plan to prove she’s the rightful successor. But in this family, ambition comes at a deadly cost. The Crown is a gripping story of power, pride, and a daughter who refuses to be overlooked.
